---
---
<section class="hero" id="inicio">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="eyebrow">🔧 Disponible en tu ciudad</span>
      <h1>¿Tuviste un problema<br/> y no supiste<br/><em>a quién llamar?</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        FixYa conecta tu emergencia en el hogar con técnicos certificados y cercanos — en minutos, no en días.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn-primary">Únete antes del lanzamiento</a>
        <a href="#servicios" class="btn-ghost">Ver servicios →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-trust">
        <div class="trust-pill">⚡ Respuesta en &lt; 15 min</div>
        <div class="trust-pill">⭐ Técnicos verificados</div>
        <div class="trust-pill">📍 Geolocalización en tiempo real</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="map-container" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="map-grid"></div>
      <div class="map-ring ring-1"></div>
      <div class="map-ring ring-2"></div>
      <div class="map-ring ring-3"></div>
      <div class="map-center">
        <span class="center-icon">📍</span>
        <span class="center-label">Tú</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-dot dot-a"><span class="dot-icon">🔧</span><span class="dot-tag">Gasfitero · 0.8km</span></div>
      <div class="tech-dot dot-b"><span class="dot-icon">⚡</span><span class="dot-tag">Electricista · 1.2km</span></div>
      <div class="tech-dot dot-c"><span class="dot-icon">🪚</span><span class="dot-tag">Carpintero · 2.1km</span></div>
      <div class="tech-dot dot-d"><span class="dot-icon">🔧</span><span class="dot-tag">Gasfitero · 3.0km</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 7rem 2rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%; left: -10%;
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(27,79,255,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10%; right: 10%;
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,92,26,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(27,79,255,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(27,79,255,0.4);
    color: #7B9FFF;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--orange); }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--orange);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, opacity 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(255,92,26,0.35);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); opacity: 0.9; }
  .btn-ghost {
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }
  .trust-pill {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }
  /* MAP */
  .map-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    max-width: 440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .map-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(27,79,255,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(27,79,255,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(circle, black 60%, transparent 80%);
  }
  .map-ring {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(27,79,255,0.2);
    animation: pulse-ring 3s ease-out infinite;
  }
  .ring-1 { width: 30%; height: 30%; animation-delay: 0s; }
  .ring-2 { width: 55%; height: 55%; animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .ring-3 { width: 80%; height: 80%; animation-delay: 1.6s; }
  @keyframes pulse-ring {
    0%   { opacity: 0.6; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(0.95); }
    100% { opacity: 0;   transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.05); }
  }
  .map-center {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    background: var(--blue);
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 52px; height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(27,79,255,0.25), 0 0 30px rgba(27,79,255,0.4);
    z-index: 10;
  }
  .center-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 1; }
  .center-label { font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .tech-dot {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    animation: dot-appear 0.6s ease both, dot-float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .tech-dot .dot-icon {
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 2px solid var(--orange);
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255,92,26,0.3);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .tech-dot .dot-tag {
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .dot-a { top: 12%; left: 55%; animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .dot-b { top: 55%; left: 72%; animation-delay: 0.9s; }
  .dot-c { top: 72%; left: 22%; animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  .dot-d { top: 20%; left: 10%; animation-delay: 2.1s; }
  @keyframes dot-appear {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.7); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  }
  @keyframes dot-float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50%       { transform: translateY(-6px); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .map-container { max-width: 320px; }
  }
</style>